-----------------Employee Management System-----------------------
Using Only Collection (List)

1.Employee Details
	-Employee Id
		-Formate - 6 Characters
				 - First 3 characters are alphabets 
				 	- First 2 characters of Name and Last Characters of Name
				 - Last 3 characters are Digits
				 
				 Ex :- Raju -- Id - Raj303
				 
	-Employee Name
	-Employee age
	-Employee emailId
	-Employee MobileNumber
	-Employee type("Developer","Tester","Hr")
	-Employee Designation
	-Employee salary
	-Employee years of Experience

2.Create a System thet can manage the Employees
	-Add an Employee , Remove an Employee,
	-Update Employee Details
	 Details that can be Updated - Moble number, EmailId,
	 Salary , Designation , Year Of Experience
	-Display all Employee Details
